                        <p><strong>HOW DOES DoFasting INTERACT WITH YOU VIA THE INTERNET?</strong></p>
                        <p>You may visit our website https://www.dofasting.com/ without identifying yourself.<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong>If
