                            <p><i><strong>Use and disclosure for administration and management</strong></i></p>
                            <p>DoFasting will also use and disclose personal information for a range of administrative,
                                management and operational purposes.&nbsp; This includes:<br>administering billing and payments
                                and debt recovery;<br>planning, managing, monitoring and evaluating our services;<br>quality
