                                <p><i><strong>Other uses and disclosures</strong></i></p>
                                <p>We may use and disclose your personal information for other purposes explained at the time of
                                    collection (such as in a specific privacy collection statement or notice) or otherwise as set
                                out in this Privacy Policy.</p>
                                <p><strong>DOES DoFasting DISCLOSE YOUR PERSONAL INFORMATION OVERSEAS?</strong></p>
                                <p>DoFasting is a global organisation and works with members, service providers, sponsors and
                                    commercial interests across the globe. It is likely that your personal information will be
                                    disclosed to overseas recipients including service providers who may handle, process or store
                                your personal information on our behalf.</p>
                                <p>The recipients of such information may be located in USA or Lithuanian.</p>
                                <p>Entities, which are related entities of DoFasting , or are otherwise affiliated with DoFasting
                                , have operations in USA and Lithuanian</p>
                                <p>We generally collect personal information about you in Lithuanian or the jurisdiction in which
                                the DoFasting affiliate you are dealing with is located.</p>
                                <p>It is likely that your personal information will be transferred outside of the jurisdiction it
                                    was collected.&nbsp; We only ever disclose your personal information outside the jurisdiction it
                                    was collected where we are permitted to do so under applicable privacy laws. Generally this
                                    means we will take reasonable steps to ensure your personal information is treated securely and
